---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import { getAuthor } from "@lib/db";

const author = await getAuthor();
---

<PageLayout
	title="About - Kunjan Dalal"
	description="Failed poet, mathematics enthusiast, functional programming evangelist, and software architect with 17+ years of experience building production systems."
	hero={{
		title: "Builder → Architect → Consultant",
		subtitle: "17+ years of building, breaking, and fixing systems",
	}}
>
	<!-- Main Story -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		{
			author?.profilePicture && (
				<div class="float-right ml-8 mb-4">
					<div class="avatar">
						<div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
							<img src={author.profilePicture} alt={author.name} />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			)
		}

		<div class="prose-custom">
			<p class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">
				I am Kunjan (<em>a.k.a. Kunjee for friends and tweeps</em>). Failed poet, mathematics
				enthusiast, functional programming evangelist, and software architecture expert with 17+
				years of industry experience.
			</p>

			<blockquote>
				Partially natural ambidextrous, a proper south paw and a true Sagittarius.
			</blockquote>

			<p>
				I am the Founder of{" "}
				<a href="https://fuzzycloud.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
					Fuzzy Cloud
				</a>, a frequent conference speaker, and an active OSS Contributor. I maintain several open
				source projects including{" "}
				<a href="https://github.com/kunjee17/awesome-fable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
					awesome-fable
				</a>{" "}
				and contribute to various Rust ecosystem projects like actix and juniper.
			</p>

			<p>
				My expertise spans mobile, web, and cloud technologies, with a particular focus on Functional
				Programming, WebAssembly, and modern web frameworks. I've worked across startups, enterprises,
				and consulting projects — building systems that handle real users, real money, and real
				problems.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Philosophy -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-display text-3xl font-bold mb-8">What drives me</h2>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display">Pragmatic Over Perfect</h3>
					<p class="opacity-80">
						I care about solutions that work in production, not academic perfection. Trade-offs are
						inevitable — the art is knowing which ones to make.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display">Cost Consciousness</h3>
					<p class="opacity-80">
						Every architectural decision has a cost — in money, complexity, or maintenance burden. I
						optimize for long-term cost, not just initial development speed.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display">Boring Reliability</h3>
					<p class="opacity-80">
						The best systems are boring. They use proven technologies, have clear failure modes, and
						don't wake you up at 3 AM with mysterious errors.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display">Learning Through Building</h3>
					<p class="opacity-80">
						I've learned more from production failures than from any book or course. Experience beats
						theory every time.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Selected Talks -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-display text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Selected Talks and Appearances</h2>

		<div class="space-y-8">
			<!-- Scaling Elm / Fable -->
			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display mb-4">
						<a
							href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P8LPIpDGcFg"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener"
							class="link link-primary"
						>
							Scaling Elm / Fable Elmish Application
						</a>
					</h3>

					<div class="aspect-video">
						<iframe
							width="100%"
							height="100%"
							src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P8LPIpDGcFg"
							frameborder="0"
							allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
							allowfullscreen
						></iframe>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- WTF# Elmish -->
			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display mb-4">
						<a
							href="https://wtfsharp.net/wtf-is-elmish"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener"
							class="link link-primary"
						>
							WTF# Elmish
						</a>
					</h3>

					<iframe
						width="100%"
						height="150"
						scrolling="no"
						frameborder="no"
						src="https://fireside.fm/s/vuYLdIIb+-tviGFwq/iframe"
					></iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Skills Matter -->
			<div class="card bg-base-200">
				<div class="card-body">
					<h3 class="card-title text-display">
						<a
							href="https://skillsmatter.com/skillscasts/13429-from-concept-to-creation-in-a-week-with-fabulous#video"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener"
							class="link link-primary"
						>
							From Concept to Creation in a Week with Fabulous
						</a>
					</h3>
					<p class="opacity-80">Skills Matter presentation on rapid mobile app development.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Open Source -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-display text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Open Source Contributions</h2>

		<div class="prose-custom">
			<p>I maintain and contribute to various open source projects:</p>

			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>
						<a href="https://github.com/kunjee17/awesome-fable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
							awesome-fable
						</a>
					</strong>{" "}
					- Curated list of Fable resources
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Rust ecosystem</strong> - Contributions to actix, juniper, and other Rust projects
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>F# ecosystem</strong> - Various Fable and F# libraries
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				Check out my{" "}
				<a href="https://github.com/kunjee17" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
					GitHub profile
				</a>{" "}
				for more.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Timeline -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-display text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Journey</h2>

		<div class="prose-custom">
			<p>
				Started as a developer, evolved into an architect, and now consulting with companies building
				serious systems. Along the way, I've:
			</p>

			<ul>
				<li>Built mobile apps used by millions</li>
				<li>Designed systems processing billions of transactions</li>
				<li>Architected healthcare and legal tech platforms</li>
				<li>Integrated AI/RAG systems for production use</li>
				<li>Mentored teams across multiple countries</li>
				<li>Spoken at conferences worldwide</li>
			</ul>

			<p>Every project taught me something. Every failure made me better.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Contact CTA -->
	<section class="text-center bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-12">
		<h2 class="text-display text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Let's work together</h2>
		<p class="text-xl opacity-80 mb-8">
			Interested in consulting, speaking engagements, or just want to chat about systems?
		</p>
		<div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
				Get in touch
			</a>
			<a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">
				View services
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
